text: Mratibu wa Mkoa wa Pwani John Elungata ametoa ripoti hiyo masaa kadhaa baada ya shambulio la kushitukiza katika eneo la Nyongoro , sehemu maarufu ambayo Al - Shabaab imekuwa ikifanya mashambulizi yanayo lenga abiria katika magari na vyombo vya usalama .
text_en: John Elungata, the Governor of the Coast Province, submitted this report a few days after the devastating incident that occurred in the Nyongoro area, a well-known place where Al-Shabaab has been committing brutal acts of violence in vehicles and security equipment.

text_en: This decision was made during the Watergate scandal revelation which led to President Richard Nixon's resignation in 1974.
